{"tid":2235164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國第二場總統候選人辯論改以網上形式舉行","createTime":"2020-10-08T12:33:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T12:38:47.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"41b2a0ffb06a671e64bcbc1c2be68e701bc21b8e","tid":2235164,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T12:33:05.000Z","msg":"美國第二場總統候選人辯論下星期四舉行，美國總統辯論委員會決定，將透過網上形式舉行，總統特朗普與民主黨候選人拜登當日不會親身到邁阿密，主持人及提問的觀眾仍會齊集在邁阿密一個表演藝術中心，透過網上形式向候選人發問。委員會解釋，今次安排是要保障所有參與人士的健康及安全。<br />\n<br />\n拜登早前曾表示，確診感染新型冠狀病毒的特朗普，如果對病毒檢測仍然呈陽性，就不應舉行辯論。他今日表示，期待再與特朗普辯論，但必須嚴格遵守防疫措施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2360748/美國第二場總統候選人辯論改以網上形式舉行\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2360748%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%A0%B4%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E5%80%99%E9%81%B8%E4%BA%BA%E8%BE%AF%E8%AB%96%E6%94%B9%E4%BB%A5%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr0Bo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=be6d3d63\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2360748/美國第二場總統候選人辯論改以網上形式舉行</a>"},{"pid":"86362b87b7a2fd671a707c40da371f962b2e2e46","tid":2235164,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T12:34:07.000Z","msg":"Trump已經話咗唔肯，要見真人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e2782acb0b43a44b587f5f0a06b83cc14deda16","tid":2235164,"uid":18012,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"86362b87b7a2fd671a707c40da371f962b2e2e46","tid":2235164,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T12:34:07.000Z","msg":"Trump已經話咗唔肯，要見真人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T12:38:47.000Z","msg":"玩視像deep fake 都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class